description:
This is a 14 minute workout called 'Replace Treadmill With This 10 Min HIIT/CARDIO Workout' from the channel THENX.
The workout falls under Cardio/HIIT and Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Warrior Workout and The Firestarter vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Join Chris Heria as he shows you how to Replace Treadmill With this 10 Min HIIT/CARDIO Workout that is going to build muscle and burn fat. Follow along with Chris as he does every exercise with you and giving you tips and the right amount of rest so you can maintain peak fat-burning conditions.
